                        </p>
                        <p class="role">Retailer</p>
                    </div>
                </div> 
            </header>
            <div class="subheader ">
                <div class="cart-header">CART ITEMS</div>
                <div class="">
                    <p>View Summary</p>
                    
                </div>
            </div>            
            <div class="cartItems">
                <div class="card flex flex-col px-5 py-3 justify-center items-center">
